blow
Homonym Number:  3
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:shearing: a stroke with the shears, a stroke of the shears (esp. long blow).


Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
